[FILE:234:descriptions/desc.single]
BSD provides the dynamic loader facilities (dlopen/dlfcn/...) in libc
itself. However, a number of applications expect these routines to be
provided by libdl. We provide a stub libdl with no subroutines to
satisfy these applications.


